Mediaset Says Executives Acted Correctly in Mediatrade Case

-- B y   D a n   L i e f g r e e n
-- 
2011-10-18T15:13:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/mediaset-says-executives-acted-correctly-in-mediatrade-case.html
Mediaset SpA (MS)  directors Pier  Silvio
Berlusconi  and Fedele Confalonieri will demonstrate their
innocence during their trial in the Mediatrade case, Mediaset
said in a statement. The fact that Prime Minister Silvio
Berlusconi was cleared in the case makes today’s indictments
“incomprehensible,” according to the statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Liefgreen at 
 dliefgreen@bloomberg.net  